description:
Falling from the Sky

Aired on 04/22/2007, Narrated by: Jonathan Aris

On 24 June 1982, British Airways Flight 9, a Boeing 747-200B, experiences St. Elmo's fire en route from Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia to Perth, Australia. A few minutes later, all four engines flame out. After descending, the crew successfully restart the engines and land safely.
